      "content": "<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div>\n    <ai-summary-widget kind=\"Post\" group=\"content.halo.run\" name=\"019cd7a6-62f4-778d-8ca2-5019bc5b65ca\" typewriter-effect=\"true\"></ai-summary-widget>\n\n    \n<p><strong>本文作者：猫猫摸大鱼 原文地址：</strong><a href=\"https://iloli.love/archives/1773144536374\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"><strong>https://iloli.love/archives/1773144536374</strong></a></p><p><strong>声明：硅基流动大模型API是按量付费的，不是免费的，只是你根据本文参与的活动可以获取代金券进行抵扣，请随时关注代金券额度</strong></p><h2 id=\"%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81-%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%2F%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E7%A1%85%E5%9F%BA%E6%B5%81%E5%8A%A8%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9E%E5%90%8D%E5%B9%B6%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E9%87%91%E5%88%B8\"><strong>一、 登录/注册硅基流动账号，实名并获取代金券</strong></h2><p><strong>点击访问 </strong><a href=\"http://to.iloli.love/siliconflow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"><strong>http://to.iloli.love/siliconflow</strong></a></p><p><strong>输入手机号，获取验证码并填写，勾选条款，点击注册/登录</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/o1xoa51f.c5x.png\" width=\"1920px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>点击访问 </strong><a href=\"https://cloud.siliconflow.cn/me/account/authentication\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"><strong>https://cloud.siliconflow.cn/me/account/authentication</strong></a><strong> ，进行实名认证</strong></p><p><strong>（因为现在硅基流动给的都是垃圾小额时限代金券，所以我懒得开新账号写实名认证的步骤了，反正也不难）</strong></p><p><strong>点击访问 </strong><a href=\"https://cloud.siliconflow.cn/me/campaigns/real-name\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"><strong>https://cloud.siliconflow.cn/me/campaigns/real-name</strong></a><strong> ，领取实名奖励的代金券</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/image-sxeW.png\" width=\"1920px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>点击访问 </strong><a href=\"https://siliconflow.cn/2026bonus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"><strong>https://siliconflow.cn/2026bonus</strong></a><strong> ，进入活动页，点击立即报名</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/wifqm3ni.0xf.png\" width=\"1733px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>显示报名成功，点击确定</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/tbffup4w.uw2.png\" width=\"462px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>然后暂时没有优惠券可以领取，因为</strong></p><h4 id=\"%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%8B%E6%9D%A5%E6%83%B3%E8%A6%81%E9%A2%86%E5%8F%96%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E4%BB%A3%E9%87%91%E5%88%B8%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%A0%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%8C%E9%BE%99%E8%99%BE%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8api%E4%BA%86%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E9%A2%86%E5%8F%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E5%85%88%E5%86%99%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%B7%B3%E8%BF%87%EF%BC%8C%E7%AD%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%E8%83%BD%E9%A2%86%E5%8F%96%E4%BA%86%E5%86%8D%E5%9B%9E%E6%9D%A5%E7%9C%8B\"><strong>接下来想要领取活动代金券，需要你搭建完龙虾调用API了才能领取，我先写在这里，可以直接跳过，等以后能领取了再回来看</strong></h4><p><strong>点击访问 </strong><a href=\"https://siliconflow.cn/2026bonus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"><strong>https://siliconflow.cn/2026bonus</strong></a><strong> ，进入活动页，下拉，找到如下图位置，点击 查看我的礼包</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/ziwmneul.lo1.png\" width=\"1158px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>可以看到代金券已经发到我的账户里了</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/mvgtd1jy.s5h.png\" width=\"1201px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/caeab1jc.ysh.png\" width=\"1151px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><h2 id=\"%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81-%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96-api-key-%E5%B9%B6%E5%B0%86%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5%E5%B0%8F%E9%BE%99%E8%99%BE\"><strong>二、 获取 API key 并将模型接入小龙虾</strong></h2><p><strong>点击访问 </strong><a href=\"https://cloud.siliconflow.cn/me/account/ak\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"><strong>https://cloud.siliconflow.cn/me/account/ak</strong></a><strong> ，点击新建API密钥，密钥描述随意，点击新建密钥</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/f2dpszps.dys.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>点击复制我们刚刚新建的API密钥</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/x1dqqe1w.rze-ZUBv.png\" width=\"1016px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>接下来，点击访问 </strong><a href=\"https://console.cloud.tencent.com/lighthouse/instance/index\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"><strong>https://console.cloud.tencent.com/lighthouse/instance/index</strong></a><strong>，进入腾讯云控制台，并直接点击我们的服务器</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/xhg32qvg.zwx.png\" width=\"1920px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>进入机器详情页后，点击 应用管理</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/aio440ig.rlm.png\" width=\"1257px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>在 模型 里点击如图位置，打开下拉框，下拉，找到 </strong><code>自定义模型</code><strong> 并点击</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/o44e4gqo.5az.png\" width=\"899px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>复制以下代码，将刚刚复制的API 密钥替换进去（注意，不要有空格）</strong></p><shiki-code variant=\"simple\" light-theme=\"github-light\" dark-theme=\"github-dark\" font-size=\"0.875em\"><pre><code>{\n  \"provider\": \"siliconflow\",\n  \"base_url\": \"https://api.siliconflow.cn/v1\",\n  \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n  \"api_key\": \"替换这几个字替换这几个字替换这几个字\",\n  \"model\": {\n    \"id\": \"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5\",\n    \"name\": \"GLM-5\"\n  }\n}</code></pre></shiki-code><p><strong>将修改后的代码粘贴到如图框里，点击添加并应用</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/crcwvlj0.3p2.png\" width=\"805px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>（如果有以下提示，检查你粘贴的代码里是否带了不该有的空格或是其它格式错误）</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/au0uhi3c.4av.png\" width=\"368px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure><p><strong>可以看到模型已经接入了</strong></p><figure data-content-type=\"image\"><img src=\"https://iloli.love/upload/image-XFsM.png\" width=\"456px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 94vw, (max-width: 768px) 92vw, (max-width: 1024px) 88vw, min(800px, 85vw)\"></figure>\n  </div></div>",
      "createdAt": "2026-03-25T04:44:33.549Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-25T04:44:33.549Z"
